Class TreeTocModel

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TreeModel
public class TreeTocModel
extends DefaultTreeModel

The only customized place the class is different from the DefaultTreeModel is the reload() method. Since a node in Toc is often removed and reconstructed, its collapsed or expanded status needs to be recorded and restored.
